{"tid":2490219,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"一個A0毒L和O4女神的故事 (2)","createTime":"2021-04-15T12:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T14:45:05.000Z","uid":394365,"like":83,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"85b96b0237b91095814896bc9240c453aa95d8bc","tid":2490219,"uid":394365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>簡介：</strong><br />\n故事男主角阿康，毒毒一名但心地善良，能否跟心儀的女神Athena開花結果？故事結局會是童話式的「有情人終成眷屬」，還是現實的無疾而終，孤「毒」終老呢？<br />\n<br />\n舊post︰一個A0毒L和O4女神的故事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2462496/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2462496/</a><br />\n<br />\n紙言：<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/i/79G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fi%2F79G&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwOTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=e1abe372\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/i/79G</a><br />\nPenana︰ <a href=\"https://m.penana.com/story/76080/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.penana.com%2Fstory%2F76080%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwOTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=12d711b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.penana.com/story/76080/</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家繼續支持，我會俾心機繼續寫落去！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577a93c398a6a9066262835f42094183405a0b29","tid":2490219,"uid":4026,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"懂不懂規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3ac17c757ca8ec045e7b8889716178ff92f2e7","tid":2490219,"uid":397110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:06:59.000Z","msg":"新post留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd8be3148da6a959dc08d50625458ad06b18d1d","tid":2490219,"uid":3